				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\kappa _{\mathrm{ph}} \rightarrow 0$$\end{document}, the total figure of merit (ZT) can be roughly approximated by its electronic contribution (ZelT\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
