The calculated HOMO and LUMO are shown in Fig. 4. To understand the origin of the modifications of the transmission caused by the doping process, the projected self-consistent Hamiltonian (PSH) eigenstates of the system are calculated. All the states are anti-symmetric in the plane of the anthracene molecule. This means that they represent π\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
